OptionParser.t' for complete documentation.

Usage: OptionParser.t <options>

Options:
  --bar      DSN bar
  --foo      DSN foo
  --help     Show this help message
  --version  Output version information and exit
  DSN values in --foo default to values in --bar if COPY is yes.

